_header: Jesu that all this world hath wrought
Subjects: Christ, prayers to; prayers, to Christ; Cross, hours of
_description: A prayer to Jesus, by Palden — seventeen irregular lines

BLRoy2Bx.First Lines:
Iesu that all thys worlde hathe wroghtHeven & erthe ye made of
                    nowght…
BLRoy2Bx.Last Lines:
…daye to dwelle in your sarvys & ffor to shewe me
                    theffowll ffende that ys my mortall enimye pater noster aue
                    maria
